'''Democratic Repabliki ya Congo''' goba '''DR Congo''', '''DRC''', ke naga lefasaneng la [[Afrika]]. DRC e bogare bodikela bja [[Afrika]], e wela seleteng sa [[Bogare bja Afrika|Bogare bja Afrika]].


DRC e agišane le :
* [[Central African Republic]] (leboa),
* [[Sudan]] (leboa),
* [[Uganda]], [[Rwanda]], [[Burundi]], [[Zambia]] le [[Angola]] (borwa),
* [[Republic ya Congo]] (bodikela), 
* [[Tanzania]] (bohlabela).

